{"tid":141764,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"致高登打手/5毛，同埋最低賤既早洩","createTime":"2017-03-03T07:36:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T20:23:56.000Z","uid":5549,"like":54,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"44abb3821e5a82a0c899ed6a76e6d5e6106d6337","tid":141764,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:36:10.000Z","msg":"估唔到早洩到今時今日都仲係咁不知悔改<br />\n向到縱容你班手下胡作非為<br />\n<br />\n我地黎得LIHKG<br />\n一早係將自己身家性命交託左比連巴<br />\n我地絕對相信連巴唔似得早洩咁卑鄙無恥<br />\n<br />\n老老實實 如果你肯一早為BAM HKG+而公開地躹躬道歉<br />\n根本就唔會搞到今時今日咁樣既局面<br />\n<br />\n到左今日高登再無高登仔係閣下咎由自取<br />\n你以為打殘LIHKG我地就會返返去你個垃圾高登只係你夢心妄想<br />\n<br />\n2016年11月出得第一個LIHKG <br />\n我地就有本事可以再出得到千千萬萬個LIHKG<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實講咁多都無謂<br />\n我地對連尼住同望遠兩位巴打係無條件信任<br />\n當中既情義係你依啲反覆無常既小人唔會明白<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n總之一句到尾<br />\n我就點都撐LIHKG"},{"pid":"2150b1959452cba92d1be52129b4fc9775778511","tid":141764,"uid":153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:38:11.000Z","msg":"高登=中共<br />\n連尼住=港獨<br />\n<br />\n根本無得鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5956605459cffcfcb3c958230c0e45fa8e239b","tid":141764,"uid":12518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:38:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6666f281567640fba5f1baba50647bcd33805088","tid":141764,"uid":1147,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"和ｂ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d85cedfa1f41ea1742959ac0dbdce658c618483f","tid":141764,"uid":5549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:40:06.000Z","msg":"我地黎得LIHKG一早係將自己身家性命交託左比連巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae15845cb0118274aeb145fc901a099f04b4f503","tid":141764,"uid":30922,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T07:41:25.000Z","msg":"ching ho ball<br />\n希望連仔ba